{
  "id": "adv_event_2301_01_02",
  "title": "スリクスと戦うつもりで",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "――ええ、そうなの。事後承諾で悪いんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Well‚ yes. I'm sorry for the after-the-fact notice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.8246937752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "葵さん、葵さん\n莉央さんは誰にお電話掛けてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san‚ Aoi-san!\nWho is Rio-san calling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.0333333333,
      "endTime": 9.7600453695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9666666667,
      "endTime": 11.166666642900001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルをするんだから\n連絡なしって訳にはいかないからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we're doing a live battle‚\nwe can't just leave without notifying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6,
      "endTime": 16.6736735345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "楽しいカウントダウンライブのはずだったのに……\nなんでこんなことになっちゃったんだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This was supposed to be a fun countdown live…\nWhy did things turn out like this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8666666667,
      "endTime": 23.5254193942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "私だってムカムカしたけど……\nやっぱりこころを止めれば良かったのかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I was furious as well…\nMaybe we should've stopped Kokoro-chan after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7333333333,
      "endTime": 29.569599753600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの？　あそこまで馬鹿にされて\nなんにもしない方が、もっとダメだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying? If we just sit there and do\nnothing after being insulted like that‚ it'd be even worse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7666666667,
      "endTime": 35.659002367599996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirはいつでも、誰の挑戦でも受ける\nそれが真の実力者。……ですよね～、葵さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir will accept any challenge anytime.\nIsn't that right‚ Aoi-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8666666667,
      "endTime": 44.3050158565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.0744050629
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "僕はどっちでも良かったんだけど\nこころと莉央が熱くなるから、仕方ないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't mind either way. But Kokoro-chan and Rio-chan\nboth got pissed off‚ so I guess we had no choice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5,
      "endTime": 51.1808841706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　莉央さんは冷静でしたけど……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Rio-san seemed calm‚ though…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3666666667,
      "endTime": 54.503197352099995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "見た目はね。でもキレる直前だったよ、あれ\n莉央とこころって、沸点の低いところが似てるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Only on the surface. She was about to lose her temper.\nThey have low boiling points‚ that's what they have in common.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7,
      "endTime": 63.8323812486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなんだ……意外です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ that's unexpected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0333333333,
      "endTime": 67.43868478140001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ～ん、つまりこころと莉央さんの気持ちは\n一つ、ってことです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ so basically‚ Kokoro and Rio-san share the\nsame feelings!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6333333333,
      "endTime": 73.4173015912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "――ええ、つい熱くなってライブバトルを\n申し込んでしまって――。こころが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Well‚ I got carried away and impulsively applied\nfor a live battle―― Kokoro-chan did it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6333333333,
      "endTime": 79.1294556935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "さりげなくこころにだけ責任をなすりつけてる！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you blaming on Kokoro!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3,
      "endTime": 82.86569151879999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "一つじゃなかったね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They weren't sharing feelings…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0666666667,
      "endTime": 85.0279138009,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9583.333333300005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "――ええ、ありがとう。じゃあ、後は私達でやるから\nみんな、OKが出たわ。ライブバトル、やるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Thank you. Well then‚ it's up to us from now on.\nEveryone‚ it's confirmed. Live battle‚ let's do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2333333333,
      "endTime": 96.3926530202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "決まっちゃいましたかぁ……\nでも、やると決めたら全力です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's settled though…\nBut once we decide to do it‚ we'll give it our all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.6,
      "endTime": 102.16444435119999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "さくっと勝たせてもらおっか\n終わったら、ホテルで年越しそばでも食べよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's beat them easily.\nAfter it's over‚ we can have New Year's soba at the hotel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3666666667,
      "endTime": 107.8750111263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "当然よ。バトルは新曲でいきましょう\nそうと決まったら、早速レッスンよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. Let's go with a new song for the battle.\nAs soon as we've decided‚ we'll start practicing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0666666667,
      "endTime": 114.70507942830001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "了解でーす。LizNoirの凄さをあの失礼な人に\n思い知らせてやりましょう。ところで莉央さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood! Let's show that rude person the true\npower of LizNoir. By the way‚ Rio-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9,
      "endTime": 123.2116548538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
